{"word":"ἀπαρτίζω","slug":"ἀπαρτίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπαρτίζω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make even, move regularly</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to get ready, complete</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to be even</i> or <i>exact</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}